    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/28f1e0b117c6b8d26bba7c791df9f34a.avif?t=1758838289\" width=616 height=144 /></span>Everseeker 是一款隐藏物品游戏，一场充满探索和发现的迷人体验。你的目标是在一个风景如画、充满可爱兔子的村庄里找到 100 只隐藏的小昆虫。所有美术均由手工精心绘制，营造出放松且沉浸式的氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抽出一点时间，沉浸在这个美妙的世界中。我们都需要偶尔放松一下，而没有什么比一款宁静又迷人的游戏更能帮助我们缓解压力了。期待与你相见 &lt;3  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/32df70dcb88ecc967c7ac748fbc385f0.poster.avif?t=1758838289\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/32df70dcb88ecc967c7ac748fbc385f0.webm?t=1758838289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/32df70dcb88ecc967c7ac748fbc385f0.mp4?t=1758838289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/e8e04770cffd521f6fd6494773d25cfe.webp?t=1758838289\" width=618 height=22 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找 100 种生物  </p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏的秘密  </p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精美的手绘场景  </p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成就系统</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >速通模式</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持手柄操作</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开发者评论</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >个性化设置</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/13b58b4c1bf349dd2c8e7ead35015d33.poster.avif?t=1758838289\" 